#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/simple_deform.rst:4
msgid "Simple Deform Modifier"
msgstr "简单变形修改器--knight翻译"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/simple_deform.rst:6
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Simple Deform Modifier allows easy application of a simple "
"deformation to an object (meshes, lattices, curves, surfaces and texts "
"are supported)."
msgstr "简单变形修改器允许对一个物体（网格、晶格、曲线、表面和文本均支持）应用简单的形变。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/simple_deform.rst:9
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Using another object, it is possible to define the axis and origin of the"
" deformation, allowing application of very different effects."
msgstr "用另外一个物体当形变的原点和轴向，可以产生很不一样的效果。"

